messages.message: In .ibflowresults how hard is it to add links to the files that get classified as other? It's odd were like here is a link to the good results but we are just going to show you a file name with no link about something irregular that happened. Also it would be to have some notion of Data Quality Passes, and a separate queue that has Reviewed. Right now it just shows a checkbox....
Eventually I would imagine you'd be able to see a queue that has reviewed and hit a button that says fire off to the downstream system (configure some sort of API hook)....
